Today’s garden haul…beets, carrots, snap peas, radishes, yellow squash and kale… one of the reasons I LOVE growing beets is because we can eat every part of the beet. Of course, the beet roots themselves are delicious, but I use the greens in salads and the stems in smoothies or chopped up in a sautéed veggie medley or stir fry…nothing wasted!

Also, all veggies taste better when I have a special garden helper working by my side! ☺️

In our latest campaign for Allegiant Air, Director @santiagosalviche designed custom airline windows in Unreal Engine. The mission was for the windows to represent moments that @carrieunderwood cherishes most.  Moments spent in her favorite places with her family, friends and fans.  Embracing the power of virtual production and Unreal Engine we were able to accomplish this beautiful spot.
 
Thanks to the vision and strategy of our friends @rrpartners and the amazing support from @allegiant.
 
We created an incredible campaign with award-winning singer & actress @carrieunderwood embarking on a captivating journey, representing a different walk of her life.
 
We are leading up to the final spot set to be shown before the big game at Allegiant Stadium in February 2024 🏈
Stay tuned!
